WEBVTT

00:07:27.684 --> 00:07:31.121
但我如此疲惫，
But now I'm so heavy,

00:07:31.121 --> 00:07:34.325
谁能给我慰藉。
nothing consoles me.

00:07:34.325 --> 00:07:37.761
我心如漂流木，
My mind floats like driftwood,

00:07:37.761 --> 00:07:41.035
狂野，任性，无助。
wayward and wild.

00:07:41.035 --> 00:07:47.582
啊～听着，宝贝。
Ah, listen, dear heart.

00:07:47.582 --> 00:07:50.717
只要你用心，
Just pay attention,

00:07:50.717 --> 00:07:54.456
从原地出发。
go right from the start.

00:07:54.456 --> 00:08:00.748
啊～听着，宝贝。
Ah, listen, dear heart.